name: Grace John
description: I am looking for a man who has some qualities similar to mine: honesty, faithfulness, care, love, optimism and understanding. I am not a gold-digger and I don’t pay attention at bank account but I do pay attention at the way a man treats me. He should be sincere, open-hearted and completely ready for a serious relationship with only one woman. I want him to be mature and generous, being able to make small surprises and to take care about his woman, being responsible for his words and promises and I want him to be completely mine! I am very affectionate, tactile and passionate and I want to give everything I have to him! I want to cuddle with my man under the blanket, watch movies and feel that my biggest dream came true! Are you still thinking if I was created for you? Send me a letter and I will prove you that you joined this site to meet namely me!
